Analyze the Problem --> Think of Solution --> Pen Down the Solution --> Code the Solution

What is Flowchart ?
-Debugging
-Language Independent
-Break down the process into smaller step [ reduce the difficulty in understanding complicated structure]
-Amazing Documentation

 Example :

   [START]                       Terminator
   [READ N]                      Input/Output
   [Let sum =0,i=1]              Process
   [Is I greater then N?]        Decision
   --->   <---                   Arrow